    </li>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 1em;">
      Attach your <strong>CV</strong> and <strong>transcripts</strong>.
    </li>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 0;">
      I carefully read every email, but due to high volume, I may not reply individually.
    </li>
  </ul>
</div>
