<h2>Current Stony Brook students
</h2>
<p>
<b>Undergraduate Students:</b> Most undergraduate students join us through existing organized research programs and courses, including <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.stonybrook.edu/commcms/ureca/">URECA</a>, <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www3.cs.stonybrook.edu/~cse327/">CSE327: Computer Vision</a>, and <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.cs.stonybrook.edu/students/undergraduate-studies/courses/cse353/">CSE353: Machine Learning</a>. 
When possible, we also participate in <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.bnl.gov/education/">BNL</a> and <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.cshl.edu/">CSHL</a>. 
You may also consider contacting Ph.D. students in my lab. 

<br>
<b>Graduate Students:</b> 
I am happy to discuss research if our interests align. Please contact me
 by email with your CV and a brief note on how our interests might 
overlap.
</p>

